{"tid":1136570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【打壓宗教】「山東第一觀音」被迫整容成孔子 村民奇招保雕像","createTime":"2019-05-03T06:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T15:43:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":194,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac0798da74f229a1ac58f813138e4a6178ea26a","tid":1136570,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"中共去年4月推出白皮書，寫明要「宗教中國化」。此後，中國寺廟掛上五星旗、拆毀露天宗教像，《寒冬》近日報道指，「山東第一觀音」被「整容」成了孔子像。<br />\n位於山東平度市開發區城東埠村聖水池民俗文化園的「山東第一觀音」，是2011年耗資約200萬元人民幣（下同，約233萬港元）雕刻而成。這座21米高的大理石聖泉觀音像，吸引不少信眾冒名前來燒香祈福。<br />\n當地村民指，中央政府去年下令，不得傳播信佛、拜觀音等封建迷信的訊息，因此要拆除觀音像。因為村委會不捨得銷毀觀音像，又不敢不執行中共意思，於是有人出「奇招」改造觀音。<br />\n村委想出，保留觀音身，冠上中國傳統文化聖人孔子的頭，經過3個多月，花約40多萬元（約47萬港元），將聖泉觀音像的頭變成孔子的頭，「聖泉觀音」4字及和觀音的蓮花底座都被打磨掉；觀音左手上的玉淨瓶改成竹簡，整個雕像由白變黑。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190503/large/1556859137_ed12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190503%2Flarge%2F1556859137_ed12.jpg&h=58328558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190503/59558220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190503%2F59558220&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=e3691efb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190503%2F59558220&h=a9b8dbb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190503/59558220</a>"},{"pid":"42207b0ff18bd0792d962605cb8969589a3519d4","tid":1136570,"uid":14983,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d49b66e3e8ad55dcc9bd1e066af968b23c42a0","tid":1136570,"uid":9726,"like":271,"dislike":1,"score":270,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:19:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1517326b7efc702e0